text: Dinant is a municipality in the Belgian province of Namur. In 2007, 13143 people lived there. It is at 50° 15 North, 04° 54 East. ==Sisters cities== * Dinan, France * Caldas da Rainha, Portugal * Hoddesdon, England * Chios, Greece * Cagayan de Oro, Philippines == References == Category:Municipalities of Namur
